_email_template_generator\" width=\"300\" height=\"176\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-63657\" srcset=\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/pmpro_email_template_generator-300x176.png 300w, http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/pmpro_email_template_generator-600x352.png 600w, http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/pmpro_email_template_generator.png 698w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />Enhance the design of your membership emails with a custom header and footer containing your site&#8217;s name, logo and link.</div><hr /></p>\n<h2>How it Works</h2>\n<p>The form below generates the code for your Email Header and Email Footer when using the <a href=\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/free-add-ons/email-templates-admin-editor/\">Email Templates Admin Editor Add On</a>. Just enter your <em>Site Name</em>, <em>Logo URL</em> and <em>Site URL</em> &mdash; the form will display an email preview and the code to copy into the appropriate fields in your membership site admin. Give it a try!</p>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t have a logo for your membership site, <a href=\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/designing-logo-wordpress-membership-site/\">see this post about designing a logo for your WordPress Membership site</a>.</p>\n<hr />\n	<h2><i class=\"fa fa-wrench\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Generate Your Email Header and Footer</h2>\n	<hr />\n	<div class=\"row\">\n		<div class=\"medium-3 columns text-right\">\n			<p><strong><label for=\"site_name\">Site Name</label></strong></p>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"medium-9 columns\">	\n			<input style=\"width:100%;\" id=\"site_name\" name=\"site_name\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Site Name\" />\n		</div>	\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"row\">\n		<div class=\"medium-3 columns text-right\">\n			<p><strong><label for=\"logo_url\">Logo URL</label></strong></p>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"medium-9 columns\">\n			<input style=\"width:100%;\" id=\"logo_url\" name=\"logo_url\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Full Logo URL - including http://\" />\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"row\">\n		<div class=\"medium-3 columns text-right\">\n			<p><strong><label for=\"site_url\">Site URL</label></strong></p>\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"medium-9 columns\">\n			<input style=\"width:100%;\" id=\"site_url\" name=\"site_url\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Full Site URL - including http://\" />\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"row\">\n		<div class=\"medium-9 medium-offset-3 columns\">\n			<button class=\"btn_primary\" id=\"updateLogo\">Preview &amp; Get the Code</button>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<hr />\n	<div class=\"pmpro_message pmpro_default\">\n		<h2><i class=\"fa fa-envelope\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Email Template Preview</h2>\n		<div style=\"background:#FAFAFA;padding:15px;text-align:center;\">\n			<table style=\"background:#FAFAFA;margin:0px;\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" height=\"100%\" width=\"100%\">\n			  <tr>\n				<td style=\"border:none;padding:0px;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\">\n				  <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border-top:2px solid #DDDDDD;border-bottom:2px solid #DDDDDD;margin:0px;text-align:left;width:100%;\">\n					<tr>\n					  <td style=\"border:none;padding:20px;\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\n						<a id=\"site_url_target_1\" href=\"http://www.yourdomain.com\" title=\"Your Site Name\" target=\"_blank\">\n						  <img id=\"logo_url_target\" alt=\"Your Site Name\" src=\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/email/images/email_default.png\" style=\"display:inline;max-height:80px;padding-bottom:0;\"/>\n						</a>\n					  </td>\n					</tr>\n					<tr>\n					  <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:none;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:23px;padding:0px 20px 0px 20px;text-align:left;\">\n						<div style=\"text-align:left;padding:20px 0px 20px 0px;border-bottom:1px solid #DDDDDD;border-top:1px solid #DDDDDD;\">\n							<p>Dear !!name!!,</p>\n							<p>Thank you for your membership to !!sitename!!. Your membership account is now active.</p>\n							<p>\n								Below are details about your membership account.<br />\n								Account: !!display_name!! (!!user_email!!)<br />\n								Membership Level: !!membership_level_name!!\n							</p>\n							<p>Respectfully,<br />!!sitename!!</p>\n						</div>\n					  </td>\n					</tr>\n					<tr>\n					  <td valign=\"top\" style=\"border:none;color:#888888;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:22px;padding:20px;text-align:left;\">\n						<p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">&copy; 2016 <a id=\"site_url_target_2\" style=\"color:#888888;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;\" href=\"http://www.yourdomain.com\"><span id=\"site_name_target\">Your Site Name</span></a></p>\n					  </td>\n					</tr>\n				  </table>\n				</td>\n			  </tr>\n			</table>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"pmpro_message pmpro_alert\">\n		<h2><i class=\"fa fa-code\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Email Template Code</h2>\n		<hr />\n		<h4>Email Header HTML</h4>\n		<span class=\"muted\"><em>Copy and paste this content into the \'Email Header\' template under \'Memberships\' > \'Email Templates\'.</em></span>\n		<textarea readonly rows=\"11\" style=\"font-size: 12px;line-height: 15px;\" id=\"email_header_html\"><div style=\"background:#FAFAFA;padding:15px;text-align:center;\"><table style=\"background:#FAFAFA;margin:0px;\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" height=\"100%\" width=\"100%\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border-top:2px solid #DDDDDD;border-bottom:2px solid #DDDDDD;margin:0px;text-align:left;width:100%;\"><tr><td style=\"border:none;padding:20px;\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"><a href=\"http://www.yourdomain.com\" title=\"Your Site Name\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Your Site Name\" src=\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/email/images/email_default.png\" style=\"display:inline;max-height:80px;padding-bottom:0;\"/></a></td></tr><tr><td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:none;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:23px;padding:0px 20px 0px 20px;text-align:left;\"><div style=\"text-align:left;padding:20px 0px 20px 0px;border-bottom:1px solid #DDDDDD;border-top:1px solid #DDDDDD;\"><p>Dear !!name!!,</p></textarea>\n		<hr />\n		<h4>Email Footer HTML</h4>\n		<span class=\"muted\"><em>Copy and paste this content into the \'Email Footer\' template under \'Memberships\' > \'Email Templates\'.</em></span>\n		<textarea readonly rows=\"6\" style=\"font-size: 12px;line-height: 15px;\" id=\"email_footer_html\"><p>Respectfully,<br />!!sitename!!</p></div></td></tr><tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border:none;color:#888888;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:22px;padding:20px;text-align:left;\"><p style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">&copy; 2016 <a style=\"color:#888888;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;\" href=\"http://www.yourdomain.com\">Your Site Name</a></p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></div></textarea>\n	</div>			\n	<script>\n	jQuery(function($) {\n		var default_header = $(\'#email_header_html\').html();\n		var default_footer = $(\'#email_footer_html\').html();\n		\n		$(\'#updateLogo\').click(function() {\n			updateTemplate();\n		});\n		\n		function updateTemplate() {\n			var site_name = $(\'#site_name\').val();\n			var logo_url = $(\'#logo_url\').val();\n			var site_url = $(\'#site_url\').val();\n			\n			//defaults\n			if(site_name == \'\')\n				site_name = \'Your Site Name\';\n			if(logo_url == \'\')\n				logo_url = \'http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/email/images/email_default.png\';\n			if(site_url == \'\')\n				site_url = \'http://www.yourdomain.com\';\n			\n			$(\'#logo_url_target\').attr(\"src\",logo_url);\n			$(\'#logo_url_target\').attr(\"title\",site_name);\n			$(\'#site_url_target_1\').attr(\"href\",site_url);\n			$(\'#site_url_target_2\').attr(\"href\",site_url);\n			$(\'#site_name_target\').html(site_name);\n			\n			var header = default_header;\n			var footer = default_footer;\n			\n			header = header.replace(/Your Site Name/g, site_name);\n			footer = footer.replace(/Your Site Name/g, site_name);\n			\n			header = header.replace(/http:\\/\\/www.yourdomain.com/g, site_url);\n			footer = footer.replace(/http:\\/\\/www.yourdomain.com/g, site_url);\n			\n			header = header.replace(/http:\\/\\/www.paidmembershipspro.com\\/email\\/images\\/email_default.png/g, logo_url);\n		\n			$(\'#email_header_html\').html(header);\n			$(\'#email_footer_html\').html(footer);\n		}\n		\n		updateTemplate();	//run once on load\n	});\n	</script>\n	\n<hr />\n<h2>Need more help?</h2>\n<p>For more information about customizing emails, <a href=\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/documentation/member-communications/\">see this documentation</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/membership-checkout/?level=6\">PMPro Core</a> and <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/membership-checkout/?level=20\">PMPro Plus</a> members can open a topic on our <a href=\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/forums/forum/members-forum/\">members forum</a> to get more help customizing your email template design.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:95:\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/generate-email-template-name-logo-member-communications/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				